  <description type="morphology">Plants 2–8 × 5–15 dm. Aerial flowering stems white-tomentose to floccose. Leaves: blade linear-lanceolate to narrowly oblong, 1.5–3.5 × (0.2–)0.3–1 cm, margins plane or infrequently revolute. Inflorescence branches tomentose, rarely floccose. Perianths white.</description>
